details.comment: The code imports numpy library, defines a complex number 'n', calculates hyperbolic tangent of 'n' and assigns the result to 'n0', then prints 'n0'.
details.content:
import numpy as np
n=1+1J
n0=np.tanh(n)
print(n0)
